{"tid":2250591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TWITTER 比FACEBOOK 更ON9! DEL APP!","createTime":"2020-10-20T08:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T09:29:05.000Z","uid":164491,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d74747400934b6779868a1fa813a8c5b7a5e7ed","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"至奇！<br />\n<br />\n各位手足 <br />\n關於TWITTER 戰線我自己有小小個人睇法<br />\n我明白要加大關注 一定數量既FOLLOWERS好緊要<br />\n但我發現你要融入呢個APP <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>&quot;手足互科&quot;既效益係好低 不斷FOLLOW 手足SHARE /同睇 同樣既文宣新聞只會令你好快放棄呢個APP</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n要認真玩呢個APP玩到好似FACEBOOK 咁出神入化 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">係要真係同自已講呢一個係一個娛樂生活APP</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要FOLLOW自已一D有興趣既野 <br />\n例如#FASHION #衣#食#住#行<br />\n慢慢係TWITTER SUBSCRIBE 一D 你有留意既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而唔係一味玩任務 咁樣係好難LAST 落去<br />\n一路娛樂LIKE下自己興趣既野 一路做做TWITTER 任務 咁先可以持之以恆去玩呢個APP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上我發現TWIITER相比其他APP既好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.\t你可以用短句分享心情 而唔需要理有冇人LIKE你<br />\n2.\t比IG更易厄LIKE <br />\n3.\tSHARE 文章比FACEBOOK 更容易<br />\n4.\t國際性好強 與其係FACEBOOK 圍爐 係TWITTER 留COMMENT 更加有力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.\t玩TWIITER 好似玩IG STORY咁<br />\n6.\t加TAG SEARCH 比IG更加容易"},{"pid":"8ddb87c20ea7649ef89af32df15397b3c526a4ac","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a471bed68f1b19689718cd96a0f32ab1abb11ae0","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4be6b91540b349143b302f195705e274007ac874","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"992a8963996ab8ed4995ad2689bda9785c61486e","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"65e13ece616ff74834f1fded021c7f8fbd875b4f","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"91e77bf16d5490f295096c8cb2e062eeab7442af","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"求正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a6197d39f2954eb97eb747723b7a600f1a2f97","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"eab05ea585c1a9a235e7c85e99a10b6e6b3ec3e8","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c0ba5d64c5cc814c6fa56bfb6813ab42fcd9f219","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4b43701d8bf267835d8ac312af81a2f150180cd2","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3ad0d552f0fe03dd64b96ea17e22851e35eebfb4","tid":2250591,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2397c88a